---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-comparison', text: 'Coverage Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'pricing', text: 'Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'network-and-claims', text: 'Network and Claims', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-should-choose', text: 'Who Should Choose Which', level: 2 },
  { id: 'verdict', text: 'Our Verdict', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Allianz Care Review', href: '/providers/allianz-care' },
  { title: 'BUPA Global Review', href: '/providers/bupa-global' },
  { title: 'Best Expat Insurance', href: '/best/expat-health-insurance' },
];

const coverageColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'allianz', header: 'Allianz Care' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'BUPA Global' },
];

const coverageRows = [
  { feature: 'Inpatient Care', allianz: true, bupa: true },
  { feature: 'Outpatient Care', allianz: true, bupa: true },
  { feature: 'Mental Health', allianz: 'Good coverage', bupa: 'Full parity' },
  { feature: 'Maternity', allianz: 'Up to $30,000', bupa: 'Up to $75,000' },
  { feature: 'Dental', allianz: 'Add-on', bupa: 'Included (Premier+)' },
  { feature: 'Vision', allianz: 'Add-on', bupa: 'Included (Premier+)' },
  { feature: 'Telemedicine', allianz: true, bupa: '24/7 Global' },
  { feature: 'Medical Evacuation', allianz: true, bupa: true },
  { feature: 'Pre-existing Conditions', allianz: 'Varies', bupa: 'Often covered' },
  { feature: 'No-Claims Discount', allianz: false, bupa: true },
];

const pricingColumns = [
  { key: 'profile', header: 'Profile' },
  { key: 'allianz', header: 'Allianz Care' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'BUPA Global' },
];

const pricingRows = [
  { profile: 'Single, Age 30', allianz: '$130-180/mo', bupa: '$200-300/mo' },
  { profile: 'Single, Age 45', allianz: '$200-280/mo', bupa: '$350-450/mo' },
  { profile: 'Couple, Age 35', allianz: '$260-360/mo', bupa: '$400-550/mo' },
  { profile: 'Family of 4', allianz: '$400-600/mo', bupa: '$700-950/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Allianz Care vs BUPA Global"
  description="Compare Allianz Care and BUPA Global international health insurance. See coverage, pricing, and which provider fits your needs."
  headline="Allianz Care vs BUPA Global: Which Is Right for You?"
  subheadline="Mid-range flexibility versus premium inclusivity. Here's how these two international health insurers compare."
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get Quotes from Both"
  ctaButtonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Allianz Care and BUPA Global both offer comprehensive international health insurance, but they take different approaches. Allianz Care offers flexibility and competitive pricing, while BUPA Global provides more inclusive premium coverage with better mental health and pre-existing condition handling.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Allianz Care</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li><strong>Network:</strong> 2M+ providers globally</li>
        <li>Flexible plan tiers (Essential to Platinum)</li>
        <li>Strong in Europe and Asia</li>
        <li>Up to 60% savings with high deductibles</li>
        <li>MyHealth digital tools</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">BUPA Global</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li><strong>Trustpilot:</strong> 4.4/5 stars</li>
        <li>Mental health parity (equal to physical)</li>
        <li>Pre-existing conditions often covered</li>
        <li>Dental/vision included in top tiers</li>
        <li>No-claims discount available</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Both Providers"
    description="Get quotes from Allianz Care and BUPA Global for your situation."
    buttonText="Get Free Quotes"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="coverage-comparison">Coverage Comparison</h2>
  <p>
    BUPA Global includes more benefits in their standard plans, while Allianz Care takes a more modular approach where you add what you need.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={coverageColumns} rows={coverageRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Key Differences</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Mental health:</strong> BUPA Global offers full mental health parity — same limits as physical health. Allianz Care covers mental health but with separate limits.</li>
    <li><strong>Maternity:</strong> BUPA Global has higher maternity limits ($75,000 vs $30,000) in comparable plans.</li>
    <li><strong>Pre-existing conditions:</strong> BUPA Global is more likely to cover pre-existing conditions from day one. Allianz Care typically requires waiting periods or exclusions.</li>
    <li><strong>Dental/vision:</strong> Included in BUPA's Premier and Elite plans. Add-on with Allianz Care.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="pricing">Pricing</h2>
  <p>
    Allianz Care is significantly more affordable than BUPA Global, typically 30-40% less for comparable coverage. This reflects BUPA's more inclusive approach.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={pricingColumns} rows={pricingRows} />
  </div>

  <p>
    <em>Prices based on comprehensive plans excluding US coverage. Your actual quote may vary based on specific plan selection, deductible, and location.</em>
  </p>

  <h3>Notes on Pricing</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Allianz Care's high-deductible options can reduce premiums by up to 60%</li>
    <li>BUPA's no-claims discount rewards claim-free years</li>
    <li>Adding dental/vision to Allianz closes some of the price gap</li>
    <li>Both charge significantly more for US coverage</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Get Your Actual Price"
    description="Estimates vary. See what you'd actually pay based on your details."
    buttonText="Get a Quote"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
  />

  <h2 id="network-and-claims">Network and Claims</h2>

  <h3>Provider Networks</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>Allianz Care</strong> has a network of over 2 million providers worldwide, with particular strength in Europe and Asia.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>BUPA Global</strong> offers access to 1.7 million providers globally, with excellent coverage in major expat destinations.
  </p>
  <p>
    Both networks are extensive. You're unlikely to have trouble finding care with either provider in popular expat locations.
  </p>

  <h3>Claims Process</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>Allianz Care</strong> processes most claims within 5 business days. Their MyHealth app allows digital claim submission and tracking.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>BUPA Global</strong> has strong claims reviews, with customers praising fast settlements. Their MembersWorld app handles claims digitally.
  </p>

  <h3>Customer Service</h3>
  <p>
    Both providers offer 24/7 multilingual support. BUPA Global includes access to in-house doctors and nurses for medical advice.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-should-choose">Who Should Choose Which</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose Allianz Care If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Budget is a primary concern</li>
        <li>You want to customize coverage</li>
        <li>You're based in Europe or Asia</li>
        <li>You prefer high-deductible options</li>
        <li>You don't have pre-existing conditions</li>
        <li>Mental health parity isn't essential</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose BUPA Global If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Mental health coverage is a priority</li>
        <li>You have pre-existing conditions</li>
        <li>You want all-inclusive benefits</li>
        <li>Higher maternity limits matter</li>
        <li>You value no-claims discounts</li>
        <li>Budget is flexible for premium coverage</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="verdict">Our Verdict</h2>
  <p>
    This comparison comes down to budget versus benefits.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Choose Allianz Care</strong> if you want solid international coverage at a competitive price and don't need the extras BUPA includes. Their flexibility and high-deductible options make them a good value choice.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Choose BUPA Global</strong> if mental health parity, pre-existing condition coverage, or all-inclusive benefits are priorities. You'll pay more, but you get a more comprehensive product with fewer surprises.
  </p>
  <p>
    For healthy expats primarily concerned with cost, Allianz Care is the better value. For those who want maximum protection and can afford it, BUPA Global delivers.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready to Decide?"
    description="Compare quotes from both providers based on your specific needs."
    buttonText="Compare Plans Now"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This comparison is for informational purposes only. Prices, coverage, and plan details change frequently. We are not insurance brokers. Verify all information with the providers before purchasing.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
